   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-1" image="QW_74.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas$<BR>Haha I knew you'd take this job! I trust you'll do a good job.<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Arnute Canyon</FONT> can be entered from <FONT color=#a82424>Tel Rosa Gates</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1024_lamia_gray-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1024_lamia_gray-1-a" mid="28" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Cursed? (Wait a minute, I didn't hear anything about that before)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Canyon Guardian Sharti$<BR>Phew… It seems like you come to this canyon very often.<BR>Are you that fond of this cursed canyon?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1024_lamia_gray-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1024_lamia_gray-1-b" mid="30" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Then please teach me~</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n1024_lamia_gray-1-b" mid="79" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Did something happen here?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Canyon Guardian Sharti$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Sharti looks at you with a stunned face)</FONT>You mean you came here without knowing what kind of place this is? I knew humans were stupid but you seem worse.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1024_lamia_gray-1-b" image="QM_black_Dragon.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1024_lamia_gray-1-c" mid="32" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Canyon Guardian Sharti$<BR>…It would not be polite to ignore those who want to learn so I'll tell you what happened.<BR>50 years ago, the humans formed a raid team to kill the Black Dragon. However, Black Dragon's blood was a poison that deformed living creatures. Some of the raiders were poisoned by the blood too.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1024_lamia_gray-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1024_lamia_gray-1-d" mid="34" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Canyon Guardian Sharti$<BR>The poisoned soldiers died while screaming in the torturous process of deformation. But humans did not know how to get rid of those horrible corpses. …They couldn't just leave them there either.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1024_lamia_gray-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1024_lamia_gray-1-e" mid="36" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Canyon Guardian Sharti$<BR>So they became interested in this deserted canyon. They made a deal with my tribe who was living here. In exchange for building a new temple for our tribe, they wanted to bury the contaminated corpses here and wanted us to stop other humans from entering.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1024_lamia_gray-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1024_lamia_gray-1-f" mid="38" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Canyon Guardian Sharti$<BR>But Black Dragon's poison was stronger than we thought. Even my tribe which was well-versed in magic became fearful of the Black Dragon's blood, and all the Lamias left this canyon except me.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1024_lamia_gray-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1024_lamia_gray-1-g" mid="40" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Then the skeletons I saw just now… Could they be...?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Canyon Guardian Sharti$<BR>Eventually, monsters who were contaminated by the Black Dragon's blood started to appear. Those monsters had lost their sanity... This canyon became a poisonous land covered with monsters and people began calling this place  the "cursed canyon".</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1024_lamia_gray-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1024_lamia_gray-1-h" mid="43" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Then...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>$Canyon Guardian Sharti$<BR>What you think is correct. But those people seemed quite unhappy when others came to their resting places. Thanks to that, I gained enough power to protect this canyon. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Sharti smiles bitterly)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1024_lamia_gray-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1024_lamia_gray-2" mid="45" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="44"><![CDATA[<html>$Canyon Guardian Sharti$<BR>I believe I have answered you enough. Intruder, no matter how good you may be, it is under the pact made by my tribe that I should not allow you in here. I will chase you out with my utmost ability if you come back again. I have warned you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1024_lamia_gray-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="46"><![CDATA[<html>$Canyon Guardian Sharti$<BR>…It has actually been a long time since I talked this much.<BR>Now go back.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Report to Saint Haven's Heraldry Scholar Stas)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-a" mid="48" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Tell him what you heard from Sharti)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas$<BR>Hahaha welcome back! I was waiting for you. Did you find out anything?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-b" mid="50" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="49"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas$<BR>What…? The soldiers who died during the Black Dragon Raid… they were buried there?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-c" mid="53" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="52"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas$<BR>Hmm well… I was wondering where they were… and they were actually asleep in that deserted canyon...<BR>Hmm... <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Stas looks bitter)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-d" mid="56" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>......</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="55"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas$<BR>Though they did not make a wrong choice in fighting with the Black Dragon, it hurts me to think that the soldiers who fought with their lives for peace are buried in a remote canyon. Was that all that we could do for them?... Ha...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-e" mid="58" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="57"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas$<BR>Is this the dark side of history…? I wish I could rebuild the temple and graves to pay respects to their souls but that would be difficult with all the monsters around. I guess the best we can do is to remember them.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-f" mid="60" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#086171>(Receive Reward)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="59"><![CDATA[<html>$Quest reward$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n088_scholar_starshy-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="61"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Stas$<BR>…Well, I should record this down first.<BR>It's good that we could learn more about <FONT color=#a82424>Arnute Canyon</FONT>.<BR>I hope there are no more cases of hidden dark historical events...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
